      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so the interior is spotless and the paint is glowing. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. You won't find a single thing out of place. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
