    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional A80-generation specimen featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six power plant with factory-spec sequential twin-turbochargers. This unit is paired with the highly sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The mechanical assembly remains in peak operational state, with pristine cylinder compression and a completely dry undercarriage free of oxidation. Every VIN tag is present across all body panels, confirming an accident-free history and structural integrity. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the precise, communicative handling and high-speed stability synonymous with this grand touring legend.",
