      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning, deep-gloss factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, featuring supple, untouched leather seating and that unmistakable new-car scent. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the mechanical performance is smooth and responsive, backed by a comprehensive, paper-documented service history from day one. This isn't just a used car; it's a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. You will not find a more preserved specimen on the market.",
